'Things are going well but there's still some room for improvement. I'm still working hard trying to prepare myself for a higher level.

'I'm feeling good and ready to continue this form.'

Liverpool's have endured a mixed start to the current season, with Saturday's 2-1 win over West Brom lifting Brendan Rodgers' side to ninth in the Premier League and ending a run of just one point from three games.

